<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 01:03:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>澳大利亚养老基金罕见地考虑提供加密货币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/australian-pension-fund-mulls-offering-crypto-in-rare-move</link><description>澳大利亚最大的养老基金之一 Hostplus 正在考虑向其成员提供加密货币作为投资选择，迄今为止，这一资产类别在很大程度上被其行业竞争对手所回避。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icuz86zYya7A/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 23:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/australian-pension-fund-mulls-offering-crypto-in-rare-move</guid></item><item><title>华尔街支持的加密货币交易所利用韩元稳定币瞄准亚洲外汇市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/wall-street-backed-crypto-exchange-targets-asia-fx-market-using-won-stablecoin</link><description>由 Citadel 证券支持的加密货币交易所正在创建第一个基于区块链的韩元兑美元衍生品，这是亚洲最繁忙的货币对之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3bAKZRADnFI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/wall-street-backed-crypto-exchange-targets-asia-fx-market-using-won-stablecoin</guid></item><item><title>Henry Kravis 支持的 ParaFi 新基金筹集 1.25 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/henry-kravis-backed-parafi-raises-125-million-for-new-fund</link><description>ParaFi 是一家总部位于纽约的数字资产管理公司，其支持者包括 KKR &amp;amp; Co. 联合创始人亨利·克拉维斯 (Henry Kravis)，该公司告诉彭博社，该公司于 3 月份为一只新风险基金筹集了 1.25 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioQXnvew3Xc4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 20:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/henry-kravis-backed-parafi-raises-125-million-for-new-fund</guid></item><item><title>特朗普给予伊朗谈判五天时间，比特币上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示美国已开始与伊朗进行谈判后，比特币与股市一起上涨，而油价下跌，这增加了人们对达成协议以缓解冲突的希望。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV70TN1fQsCU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 11:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>瑞士私人银行王朝因加密战略冲突而分裂</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</link><description>瑞士私人银行王朝正因公司未来愿景的不同代际分歧而陷入痛苦之中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioWHn.dGWqDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 05:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</guid></item><item><title>战争紧张局势加剧不确定性，比特币跌至两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-war-tensions-fan-uncertainty</link><description>比特币周一在两周低点附近波动，在亚洲早盘交易中下滑，然后在中东紧张局势升级之际反弹至关键支撑位。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZacU6KS4JyU/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 07:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-war-tensions-fan-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>由于战争担忧影响加密货币市场，比特币跌破 69,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-22/bitcoin-drops-below-69-000-as-war-fears-weigh-on-crypto-markets</link><description>随着美国、以色列和伊朗相互威胁和攻击，比特币和其他加密货币再次下跌。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBbzxqa3bbmU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 13:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-22/bitcoin-drops-below-69-000-as-war-fears-weigh-on-crypto-markets</guid></item></channel></rss>